Settings:
* Condition Card layout: condition_tile
* Condition Card color: condition_card_background
* Search and Condition/Sugestion Card background color: suggestion_condition_background
* Cardview
  Modify layout/suggestion_condition_container.xml to get rid of elevation
  <attr name="cardBackgroundColor" format="color" />
  <color name="cardview_dark_background">@*android:color/transparent</color>
  <style name="CardView" parent="@*android:style/Widget">
   <item name="cardBackgroundColor">*android:color/transparent</item>
  </style>
* Search toolbar is controlled by colorBackground in main settings style,
  settings_main_dashboard layout, and search_panel layout.
* Wifi icon detail color wifi_details_icon_color.
